text: Stinsen Arena is an indoor bandy venue in Nässjö in Sweden. Construction began on 27 April 2012. The arena was opened on 6 October 2012. The first game inside the arena was played on 11 October 2012. In that game, Nässjö IF lost, 2-7, to Vetlanda BK. ==References== Category:Bandy in Sweden Category:2012 establishments in Sweden Category:Buildings and structures in Sweden
title: Stinsen Arena
